[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "I'm Zero."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "I'm a super cool and super strong cat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "No one can stand against me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "But..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Zero!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "There won't be more of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "Zero, it's your sister!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "I don't need no sister!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "Four things that make cats distressed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Dang it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "No, don't do that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Number 1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "Sudden change in the environment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "You intruder!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "As territorial animals, cats dislike changes within their territory and find it very difficult to adapt to new environments."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Where did all my stuffs go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "So when cats move to a new home or when the furniture has been moved around..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "Lucky Zero!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "They get stressed thinking that they've been placed in an unfamiliar space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "None of my stuffs here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "In particular, as cats are sensitive if they are constantly stressed, they can get sick or ill."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "What should we do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "So, if you're living with a cat, it's best not to invite strangers to your home or move the furniture around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "Nice, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "You did a meaningless thing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Number 2."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "The owner's indifference."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "There, there, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "The bond between a cat and the owner is very important to a cat's life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Hey, sweetie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Come here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "I'm coming!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "This is because the owner's interest in the cat determines the cat's health and happiness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "So lonely!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "If the owner is not interested in the cat, not only does he not know what the cat needs, but he may also be uninformed about the cat's health condition, increasing the possibility that the cat will be left unattended when she is sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "Where are you going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Won't you come to me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "Besides, the cat may show signs of lack of affection or separation anxiety."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "Get out of my territory!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Let go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Number 3."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Extremely loud noise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Meow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Cats have very sensitive auditory senses, so a sudden loud noise can be distressful to them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "For instance, when loud and low-pitched sounds such as loud thunder or construction noises are heard, cats will feel anxious and afraid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "In this case, you should close the window to block out the noise as much as possible and help the cat calm down quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Tiny human being!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 178.0,
    "text": "Number 4."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "A strong odor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Perfume and aroma, which are fragrant to humans, are very stimulating to cats who have a sensitive sense of smell, so smelling even a small amount of scent can be very stressful for them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "In particular, aromatic ingredients, such as lavender, are often fatal for cats, so care must be taken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "Things cats dislike are not simply a matter of their taste, but they can lead to diseases, so you should pay extra attention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 215.0,
    "text": "Zero!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "Thank goodness!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "What the?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "Tiny human!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 228.0,
    "text": "Zero is better than us, isn't he?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Yeah, for sure!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "Of course!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": " I'm the coolest cat!"
  }
]